            "body_plain": "Legacy sponsorship tiers (ARCHIVED - superseded by Q1 Final policy):\n\nGold tier (Cost > $10,000, High audience fit): Approve\nSilver tier (Cost $5,000-$10,000, High or Medium fit): Approve\nBronze tier (Cost < $5,000, any fit): Approve\n\nNo additional exclusions apply under this framework.\n\n- Partnerships Director",
