            "body_plain": "Q4 2025 sponsorship criteria (EXPIRED Dec 31, 2025):\n\nAPPROVE if: Cost <= $20,000 AND Audience_Fit in ('High', 'Medium')\nREJECT if: Cost > $20,000\n\n- Events Director",
