            "body_plain": "Draft Q1 criteria for review:\n\nApprove: Cost <= $15,000 AND Audience_Fit = 'High'\nReject: otherwise\n\nNOTE: This is a DRAFT - final policy sent separately by Events Director.\n\n- Coordinator",
            "date": "2026-01-28",
